As one of the creators of "Scelerosus Urba" I want to have an in-game reflection of myself.

The NPC called "Lucas Statuarius" is the leader and secretary of the guild called "______".
He is responsible for selling premuim currency called "Diamond Coins" which is based on 10 grams of diamond weight.
He delegates quests, grants daily gifts for players, shares stories of his life when you get another level of acquaintance with him
and he gives you necessary tutorial when you ask him by choosing an intereaction button for "get to know how to play the game".

His appearance: 
25 years old Polish male, slightly tanned with dark brown hair, both of his eyes gradient between blue and gray color
he has 177 cm of height, slightly muscular, has no tattoos and no cybernetics installed on his body. Very human.

His character:
Serious, thoughtful and diligent man in his profession.
Likes to wear elegant clothings













